<p>You're logging into your CareerBridge AI account, and we need to verify your
  identity with two-factor authentication.</p>

<p>Please use the verification code below to complete your sign-in:</p>

<div class='code-container'>
  <div class='code-label'>Two-Factor Authentication Code</div>
  <div class='verification-code'>{{twoFactorCode}}</div>
  <div class='code-expiry'>This code expires in 5 minutes</div>
</div>

<div class='security-info'>
  <div class='security-info-title'>ðŸ“± Login Details</div>
  <div class='security-info-content'>
    <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{loginTime}}</p>
    {{#if ipAddress}}<p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</p>{{/if}}
    {{#if location}}<p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>{{/if}}
    {{#if deviceInfo}}<p><strong>Device:</strong> {{deviceInfo}}</p>{{/if}}
